### âœ… & Watch ì‚¬ìš©ë²•

#### Vue2

{% raw %}

```vue
<script>
    export default {
        data () {
            return {
                num: 0
            }
        },
        watch: {
            num (newVal, oldVal) {
                console.log(`${newVal} ${oldVal}`)
            }
        }
    }
</script>
```

{% endraw %}

#### Vue3

{% raw %}

```vue
const num = ref('')
watchEffect(() => {
    console.log(num.value)
})
```

{% endraw %}
